{"ts":"2026-07-21T22:11:14.317Z","author":"codex-root","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/1","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-21T22:11:14.317Z","author":"codex-root","text":"Evidence: implemented stable PmCliError code merge_git_config_unwritable with runtime telemetry classification and recovery context; reordered fence publication behind successful clone-local Git configuration; documented read-only behavior. Focused merge-safety and telemetry-classification tests pass. Full coverage reports 41028/41028 statements, 28854/28854 branches, 8327/8327 functions, and 39908/39908 lines (100/100/100/100). pnpm lint, typecheck, build, audit, and security scan pass. Packed-package temp consumer proved a real .git/config.lock failure exits 5, emits the stable code and dry-run guidance, leaves .gitattributes absent, succeeds after unlock, validates cleanly, and exports runMergeInstall from the public SDK."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-21T22:11:14.317Z"}],"before_hash":"84e5d4cc800eeb36c5ae3ecd9e7734530c1893b9283c2726ac78d5c1c10471f3","after_hash":"45c8d7d5f477157b69137d0d46fb411b1889c8641dcd6a5d1b11bcba56040fe8"}
